      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 06:03:19 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/670f50113d663.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/66270cd61861c.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/670f519e9dae1.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/670f504fb25dd.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6710788d54089.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6710789b00b24.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/670f50651748b.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/670f50a8ce284.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/670f50b53a188.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/670f61f36b990.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Dragon Master Armor&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Added a few small improvements&lt;br&gt;- weapon is standalone&lt;br&gt;- armor can be found on the map&lt;br&gt;- added tags, gamedata, attachment files &lt;br&gt;- fixed belt clipping&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;General update, same sick armor &amp;lt;3&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Added a second version which adds nearly all the different effects in the game to one set of armor, very OP.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;Thank &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1797815"&gt;Arch Leaders&lt;/a&gt; for the original Models and Hero Bunker &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/416599"&gt;mod&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;This is only the armor and weapon from above mod.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Armor and weapon are standalone&lt;br&gt;    20 defense each&lt;br&gt;    Attack Up, speed boost&lt;br&gt;    Increased durability&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Armor and Weapon can be found in a well just northeast of Coliseum.&lt;br&gt;Purchase gear from Cormus the&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt; traveling wagon salesmen.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;Cormus can be found near Riverside Stable and on various roads nearby.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Mod was built and test on Switch and Yuzu 1.2.1&lt;br&gt;Please use Tkmm for other versions &lt;br&gt;Include tkcl info file for easy merging&lt;br&gt;Mod requires higher priority &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor SelectedElement"&gt;Thanks TotK/BotW community for help/teaching&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Special Thanks to everyone developing tools &lt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Thanks Nintendo for making this all possible&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;First version &lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;- attack up effect&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Second version&lt;/span&gt; &lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Head&lt;/span&gt; (QuietnessUp)&lt;br&gt;- QuietnessUp&lt;br&gt;- ClimbSpeedUp&lt;br&gt;- DivingMobilityUp&lt;br&gt;- ResistElectric&lt;br&gt;- AttackUpThunderstorm&lt;br&gt;- ChargePowerUpThunderstorm&lt;br&gt;- ResitLightning&lt;br&gt;- DecreaseSwimStamina&lt;br&gt;- ClimbWaterfall&lt;br&gt;- NoSlip&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Upper&lt;/span&gt; (ResistCold)&lt;br&gt;- AttackUp&lt;br&gt;- DefenseUp&lt;br&gt;- ResistCold&lt;br&gt;- AttackUpCold&lt;br&gt;- MiasmaGuard&lt;br&gt;- ChargeSpeedUp&lt;br&gt;- DecreaseChargeAttackStamina&lt;br&gt;- AttackUpBone&lt;br&gt;- LightFootprints&lt;br&gt;- ChargePowerUpCold&lt;br&gt;- ResistFreeze&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;lower&lt;/span&gt; (ResistHot)&lt;br&gt;- AllSpeed&lt;br&gt;- ResistHot&lt;br&gt;- AttackUpHot&lt;br&gt;- SwimSpeedUp&lt;br&gt;- ExStaminaMaxUp&lt;br&gt;- ChargePowerUpHot&lt;br&gt;- NoBurning&lt;br&gt;- SandMoveUp&lt;br&gt;- SnowMoveUp&lt;br&gt;- NightMoveSpeedUp&lt;br&gt;</description>
