    <item>
      <title>Edge of Darkness 1.2.1</title>
      <author>heydo6</author>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/516412</link>
      <comments>https://gamebanana.com/mods/516412#PostsListModule</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">d2ceb90c405502adb35c1422be32b568fd51e911</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 23:28:51 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/670b4c46087e2.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/670b32b83a652.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/670b32f5ecf90.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/670b3302d4e14.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/670b333f74988.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/670b33860e7f1.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/670b33b739f6d.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/670b342a4f0b2.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/670c4fe95ef79.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/670c501bbfd2b.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/670c52a84ee4c.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; Edge of Darkness&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;I've made a lot of small improvements and added a couple new weapons&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Everything tested and working fine on Yuzu and Switch &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This mod needs higher priority on tkmm with mods that edit map files like CM and SQ&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;All weapons and enemies have custom actors with many improvements&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The three cave locations are edited to include many extra items and weapons &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Everything respawns with a Bloodmoon &lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Edge of Darkness &lt;/span&gt;Update/Rework...&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Mod adds 13 weapons and a few enemies to three different caves&lt;br&gt;Caves are loaded with extra items, material, weapons&lt;br&gt;Each cave location can be found in the first video&lt;br&gt;Weapons can also be purchased at &lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Riverside Stable&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Edge of Duality&lt;/span&gt; has Ancient Arrow type effect&lt;br&gt;All Weapons have corresponding elemental effects&lt;br&gt;Added dragon parts to Blupee Rabbit drop table&lt;br&gt;All weapons have increased durability&lt;br&gt;This mod should have high priority &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Tkmm info&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; file&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt; included&lt;/span&gt; for easy merging &lt;br&gt;Created and tested for Switch and Yuzu on 1.2.1 &lt;br&gt;For other version please use &lt;a href="https://tkmm.org/" target="_blank"&gt;Tkmm&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;Check out TotK &lt;a href="https://discord.gg/yJrtEV8W" target="_blank"&gt;Discord&lt;/a&gt; for any help &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Thanks &lt;a href="https://sketchfab.com/3d-models/ice-sword-931fed1aeedc4d6baf39a58b120c7e95" target="_blank"&gt;Sketchfab&lt;/a&gt; for the additional weapon &lt;a href="https://sketchfab.com/3d-models/autumn-sword-28c2c7262e334e529709fb88e019a716" target="_blank"&gt;models&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;br&gt;I'll also include them in a large weapon pack very soon. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor SelectedElement"&gt;Thanks everyone at TotK/BotW community for help/teaching.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;Special Thanks to everyone developing tools &lt;3.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Thanks to Nintendo for making this all possible.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
